\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 And you're married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 I am.
