Well - they sort of didn't like it but then if they next time they knew then they shouldn't - give it us you know, because - I never liked tomatoes see, like that. Oh they were - very good like that you know, mum was you 
know, she'd make sure then that - we'd have - we'd have something we liked, because I've never eaten pork in my life. I wouldn't touch it. No. So my mum used to have a little - piece of meat for me on my own always. Yes. Never liked pork.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 So if she cooked pork for the family she'd cook you something else?
