\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 If there was something on the table you wanted, like the salt, could you ask for it or did you have to wait until it was offered to you?

