\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Did all the family sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Only certain times, you know, as I was saying, yes, because -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Did you have the same places at the table?
