\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Oh th
e child - Min and I first. Always, yes, and dad after like, well you know, do the four together like, and then my aunt and my - cousin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 You were the youngest one so you wouldn't remember what happened before you could feed yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 
Yes. Mum was lovely. Very nice. Quiet, very quiet mother. And very - well, what shall I say, mum was very - sort of well educated like you know in her - she could - she was - really marvellous when she wanted t
o describe anything or if she wanted to speak or that - she was good like that you know. She used to take part in chapel you see a lot. And they used to sing a lot, my father and her you see. In chapel Yes. They go about singing anywhere they used to, yes
. Yes. Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Your father had a tenor voice, and your mother?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Mum was soprano. And my sister had a very nice voice, contralto. Yes. Lovely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 You used to make a lot of music did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 She was - she - she was three choirs - in three
 choirs at the same time Min was, yes. I wasn't so very fond of choirs, I was in the children's choir with - Lumley, Mr Lumley in - in - Ynysgaeth, that's where we used to go, Ynysgaeth - the - in Merthyr. And - well we used to go Band of Hope you know as
 they are, used to have Band of Hope first and then the singing after. Yes. But our lives really were all in the church, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Did your mother show you affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Yes. She was very very affectionate, fair play, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 If you had any worries could you share them with her or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 
Oh yes. Had to tell her everything, she could tell by us very often now you know, she always used to say that, come on, come on what is it, you know. YES. Marvellous at that she was, fair play, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 What about your father, was he an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Yes, he was very good dad was. Yes, fair play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Did he show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 If you had any worries could you share them with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 We could, yes, but he'd give us more worri
es than we give him very often you know. Yes. Always used to pull his leg you know, yes, fair play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 How did your parents expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Well we tried to do our best. You know like. If we done anything wrong mother soon - only
 a - only look at us, that's all mum would do, that was enough you know like, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your sister in certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Well - how shall I put that now, mum used to say, now - she always wanted us to go tog
ether. No mind what friends we had, how many, but always bring 'em home, you know. And never mind where you go, what you do, bring '-em home, let me see who so and so, you know, of years ago, and out in the country you see we had to be so careful. Like as
 mother - if we weren't home in the night mum was with her shawl and out meeting us always you know. Watching us whatever we were doing, she - she was wonderful like that, fair play.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 Did they say you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10838799 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 
Well my mother used to tell us to be careful what we're doing and go the other way, her way, so if - don't never go up against them again, try and go the other way, she always used to say you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12022365 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2901470\charrsid10176723 What kind of people do you think - your parents hoped you would grow up to be?
