Now how can - well I think they wanted really us to follow them, you know, in a sense because I mean they were pretty good themselves and I think they wanted us to be the same you know, that's how they were watching us 
so much I think. 'Cos years ago they did didn't they? You know, you shouldn't go out of their sight should you. No.
